\
The script:  Temptation => Desire => Sin => Death\
\
When we know the script we can predict with great accuracy where the story will end up.\
\
This why others can give such great advice. We all know the script. Do the right things and normally (I know there are exceptions to every rule) the right things happen. Eat healthy and normally you get healthier. Speak life into and guide your kids with discipline and normally they turn out right. Hang out with 3 people who not really good for you and normally you become the 4th person who isn't good for others. \
\
This is great news if you think about. While all of us are blind in some ways to our own disfunction there is a solution. We can ask the right people around us who really know and love us what they see that we don't. We don't have to walk through life hoping we are going in the right direction. We can know.  \
\
So in a last ditch effort to help you find what alligators might be lurking underneath the dark water of your soul, I want to encourage you to find someone you trust. Ask them what they see in your life that you are justifying, excusing, or explaining away that is either hurting you or will in the future.\
\
It's easy to see others future by their current decisions, but it is hard to see our own. We need people in our lives to help us see what we can't see and then in turn have the ability to do what we need to do.\
\
Who can you talk to? Do you have a person? A spouse, a friend, a pastor or mentor? If you do make the decision today to discuss this chapter with them. For those that don't know how or what that would look like here is how it might go:\
